  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">The Penrose dodecahedron and the Witting polytope are identical in <math altimg="si1.gif" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><msup><mrow><mi mathvariant="double-struck">CP</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup></math></subfield>
